    <h1 class="page-header__title">Major Ports of India</h1>
    <p class="page-header__subtitle">13 notified major ports (12 operational + Galathea Bay). Key distinctions, legal framework, cargo rankings, Sagarmala 2.0, and exam traps. Updated to April 2026.</p>
